⁦🎙️ Mikel⁩ Arteta (Arsenal): &quot;Manchester City's ban overturned? There is no question about what happened. They completely deserve to be in [the] UCL because what they&rsquo;ve done on the pitch is unquestionable and the regulators have looked at it and have decided that they haven&rsquo;t done anything wrong.&quot;<br />
<br />
&quot;So you have the two aspects that are really clear and transparent and they&rsquo;re going to be in Champions League because they deserve [it] for what they do on the pitch and what they do outside the pitch..&quot;
